metrics.visualTitle: New Cases by Year and Top 5 Countries

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Europe"}, 'Covid final'[Continents])

	VAR __SQDS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Covid final'[Countries],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"SumNew_Cases2", CALCULATE(SUM('New cases'[New Cases]))
		)

	VAR __SQDS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(5, __SQDS0Core, [SumNew_Cases2], 0)

	VAR __ScopedCoreI0 = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'LocalDateTable_a42d3b72-6d57-4238-adf3-53bc350dd10c'[Year],
			'Covid final'[Countries],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__SQDS0BodyLimited,
			"SumNew_Cases2", CALCULATE(SUM('New cases'[New Cases]))
		)

	VAR __ScopedCoreDM1 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				FILTER(
					KEEPFILTERS(
						SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
							'LocalDateTable_a42d3b72-6d57-4238-adf3-53bc350dd10c'[Year],
							__DS0FilterTable,
							__SQDS0BodyLimited,
							"MinDate", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('LocalDateTable_a42d3b72-6d57-4238-adf3-53bc350dd10c'[Date]))),
							"CountRowsLocalDateTable_a42d3b72_6d57_4238_adf3_53bc350dd10c", CALCULATE(COUNTROWS('LocalDateTable_a42d3b72-6d57-4238-adf3-53bc350dd10c'))
						)
					),
					NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_a42d3b72-6d57-4238-adf3-53bc350dd10c'[Year]))
				)
			),
			"'LocalDateTable_a42d3b72-6d57-4238-adf3-53bc350dd10c'[Year]", 'LocalDateTable_a42d3b72-6d57-4238-adf3-53bc350dd10c'[Year],
			"MinDate", [MinDate]
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__ScopedCoreI0,
			__ScopedCoreDM1
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryDbCount = 
		CALCULATE(
			COUNTROWS(
				SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'LocalDateTable_a42d3b72-6d57-4238-adf3-53bc350dd10c'[Year])
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryDbCount = 
		CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Covid final'[Countries])))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			[MinDate],
			[SumNew_Cases2],
			350,
			'Covid final'[Countries],
			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0BodyBinnedSample, 'Covid final'[Countries])

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
			__DS0BodyBinnedSample,
			"ColumnIndex",
			__DS0SecondaryBase,
			'Covid final'[Countries],
			ASC
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
		"DS0PrimaryDbCount", __DS0PrimaryDbCount,
		"DS0SecondaryDbCount", __DS0SecondaryDbCount,
		"DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0SecondaryBase

ORDER BY
	'Covid final'[Countries]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_a42d3b72-6d57-4238-adf3-53bc350dd10c'[Year], [ColumnIndex]

metrics.visualTitle: Sum of median_age by Continents and Countries

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
		TREATAS({"Europe"}, 'Covid final'[Continents])

	VAR __SQDS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Covid final'[Countries],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"SumTotal_Cases", CALCULATE(SUM('Covid final'[Total Cases]))
		)

	VAR __SQDS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(20, __SQDS0Core, [SumTotal_Cases], 0)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Covid final'[Continents],
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Covid final'[Countries], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
			__DS0FilterTable,
			__SQDS0BodyLimited,
			"Summedian_age", CALCULATE(SUM('Covid final'[median_age]))
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
			"'Covid final'[Continents]", 'Covid final'[Continents],
			"'Covid final'[Countries]", 'Covid final'[Countries],
			"Summedian_age", [Summedian_age]
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM1 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
			"'Covid final'[Continents]", 'Covid final'[Continents],
			"SortBy_DM1_0", [Summedian_age]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Covid final'[Continents]),
			__DS0CoreTableByDM1
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(201, __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns, [SortBy_DM1_0], 0, 'Covid final'[Continents], 1)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'Covid final'[Countries])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'Covid final'[Countries], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'Covid final'[Countries],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'Covid final'[Countries]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM1_0] DESC, 'Covid final'[Continents], [ColumnIndex]
